data.description: Updated home in central Bismarck with attached 1 car and detached 2 car garage. This home has been well maintained! The main floor of the home has a large living room with fireplace, updated kitchen with stainless appliances, large primary bedroom and extra bedroom, full bath, a large office/den with a wood burning fireplace and an area that could be utilized as an office or small rec room area. The lower level of the home has 2 non-conforming bedrooms, 1 is currently being used as a game room. There is a large laundry room, 1/2 bath and large storage/utility room with.  The quiet back yard is fully fenced with a gate that opens to a camper pad for winter storage and very private. Call for a showing today!
